Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.02,0:00:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi Haneoka is 14 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.03,0:00:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,By day, she is a happy student of\NSt. Paulia School.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.17,0:00:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But at night, she becomes the thief,\NSt. Tail, to do good deeds...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.31,0:00:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,for all who ask for help from Seira,\Na nun in training.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.22,0:00:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking to capture the elusive St. Tail\Nis an amateur detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.46,0:00:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and Meimi's classmate, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And Meimi? She may have more than a bit\Nof interest in such a determined boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.88,0:00:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I Hate Wedding Veils
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.73,0:00:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.90,0:00:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going home?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.84,0:00:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.14,0:00:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!\NNow that it's decided, let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.10,0:01:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! It's already full!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.17,0:01:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure is popular.\NShall we come another day?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.38,0:01:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.18,0:01:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't get any last time and today,\NI wanna eat some chocolate chip!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.83,0:01:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're acting very immature.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.03,0:01:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, just like a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.24,0:01:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Your obsession with ice cream\Nproves your lack of maturity.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep your opinion to yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.62,0:01:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's popular with\Ncollege girls, too, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.72,0:01:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Those college girls\Nare just as immature as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.33,0:01:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Just who are "you" calling immature?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.54,0:01:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Look who's talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.77,0:01:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're barely out of diapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we teach him\Nhow to have fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.12,0:01:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I... Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.38,0:01:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.62,0:01:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Heaven's punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.26,0:02:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.23,0:02:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.13,0:02:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.20,0:02:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.53,0:02:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.91,0:02:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.05,0:02:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.02,0:02:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.16,0:02:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.37,0:02:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.91,0:02:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.74,0:02:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter Meimi?\NYou don't look very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.75,0:02:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The happiness of a family\Ncomes from healthy greetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.49,0:02:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try again!\NWelcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.83,0:02:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.11,0:02:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,My new trick...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.30,0:03:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like she's in a bad mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.53,0:03:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she did badly on a test?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.57,0:03:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that jerk's problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.65,0:03:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ruby, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.56,0:03:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to snap at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.64,0:03:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I so irritated?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.24,0:03:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not supposed to\Nmean anything to me and still...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.13,0:03:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.23,0:03:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even know why I feel this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,How annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.90,0:04:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,God, please grant my wish.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.38,0:04:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.78,0:04:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.69,0:04:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, how beautiful!\NIt's a wedding veil, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.17,0:04:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.44,0:04:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa, why is it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.08,0:04:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.85,0:04:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it make you happy, Sayaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.02,0:04:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The wedding veil is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.52,0:04:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.39,0:04:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a gift from your fiance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.54,0:04:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it wonderful, Sayaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.34,0:04:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.73,0:04:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi, Seira, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.04,0:04:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter Meimi?\NYou don't look too happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.25,0:04:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she's found\Nthat special someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it? Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.23,0:05:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is an important day...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.43,0:05:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but you haven't prepared\Nfor it at all, am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.04,0:05:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.61,0:05:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! I haven't prepared either!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.35,0:05:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you're well prepared,\Naren't you, Seira?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.12,0:05:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Studying is something\None must do on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.06,0:05:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just how she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got ten minutes\Nuntil class starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.74,0:05:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse us...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.65,0:05:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Seniors...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.15,0:05:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the badminton club freshmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.55,0:05:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't they cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.12,0:05:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... that girl is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Sayaka Shinomiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.73,0:05:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She's cute and really popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.70,0:05:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear she lives in an\Nold mansion at the edge of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I wonder what\Nshe's staring at so intensely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.63,0:05:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.\NShe's staring pretty hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.84,0:06:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So the wedding veil is a\Ntoken of your engagement?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.95,0:06:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but...\NI've never even met him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My parents arranged\Nthe engagement themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.44,0:06:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.31,0:06:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There's someone else I'm in love with!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.31,0:06:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be engaged\Nto a stranger!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.98,0:06:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If only that veil would disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.33,0:07:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.67,0:07:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Please give me the strength\Nto dissolve this engagement.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,May the blessings of God be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.03,0:07:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's nothing\NSayaka can do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.80,0:07:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.87,0:07:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! St. Tail shall steal\Nthat wedding veil!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.29,0:07:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if the person Sayaka\Nis in love with is Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.30,0:07:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Gross! What terrible taste!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.57,0:07:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.64,0:07:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you asking\Nme something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you don't mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!\NSt. Tail never has second thoughts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.93,0:07:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll steal that wedding veil,\Nno matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.60,0:07:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see, they completely\Ndisregarded a young girl's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.73,0:08:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unforgivable.\NIsn't that right, Ruby?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,"Tonight, I'm going to steal a\Nwedding veil from...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.42,0:08:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the Shinomiya residence."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.86,0:08:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.76,0:08:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's all that noise\Nthis early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.34,0:08:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a vocal warm up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it.\NMusic doesn't run in our family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.71,0:08:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.12,0:08:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I told her to\Nkeep me informed, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.87,0:09:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I won't wash my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.15,0:09:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing?\NHurry up and eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.09,0:09:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I made a really good\Nsunny-side-up egg today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.33,0:09:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want any.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.40,0:09:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,When you make them, you grumble\Nif anything is left on the plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.48,0:09:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.65,0:09:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A growing boy like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.82,0:09:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If I eat, the note might dissapear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.16,0:09:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I've just got some stuff going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.10,0:09:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What, you found yourself a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.67,0:09:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don 't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.74,0:09:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you keep your back turned?\NWhen you talk to somebody, face them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got stuff going on so... see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.17,0:10:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that really St. Tail's note?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.74,0:10:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're a real idiot, having slept\Nthrough her writing it on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.48,0:10:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.68,0:10:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me touch it real quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid! Don't touch it!\NYour hands are dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.56,0:10:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How silly...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.66,0:10:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.73,0:10:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out, you idiot! Knock it off!\NShe's mine! I'm gonna get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.24,0:10:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.85,0:10:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.42,0:10:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if the person Sayaka\Nis in love with is Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.41,0:10:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.68,0:10:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.75,0:10:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:11:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...therefore I'd appreciate\Nyou letting me stake the place out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.04,0:11:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.21,0:11:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.92,0:11:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.45,0:11:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail has never gone back\Non a warning or failed in a caper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.17,0:11:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If you take her lightly,\Nyou'll be in a terrible situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.98,0:11:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go over the\Nplan for this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.78,0:11:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of getting the veil stolen,\NI can win over Asuka Jr., too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.82,0:11:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If this is the case, I wish\NMiss Thief could come every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.24,0:11:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, time to work.\NGotta help those in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.90,0:11:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.64,0:11:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I heard\Nsomething in the yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.58,0:11:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I think someone's out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.69,0:12:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,In situations like this\Nit's usually a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.93,0:12:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Meow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.60,0:12:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. Just a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.61,0:12:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,She's my daughter, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.18,0:12:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.42,0:12:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.99,0:13:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.80,0:13:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really going Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.41,0:13:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were Sayaka, I wouldn't want\Nan engagement like that, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.72,0:13:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If the veil is returned, I'm sure\Nthe engagement will be called off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do it, St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Without a doubt, if it's God's will!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.11,0:13:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This "Tail" thief is probably thinking\Nof entering through the attic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm going to stand watch in the room\Ndirectly below the attic, for an ambush.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.47,0:13:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But, what if she enters\Nfrom a different place?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.98,0:13:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If I say she's coming through here,\Nthat's how it will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.55,0:13:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I've met up with her many times\Nand I know what to expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.89,0:14:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you absolutely sure it's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.67,0:14:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa, don't be rude to Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.58,0:14:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa, Mama, will you wait outside?\NAsuka and I will keep watch here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.19,0:14:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.96,0:14:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.76,0:14:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll be able to catch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What's all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, just watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.22,0:14:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail never steals without a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.07,0:14:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would she want\Nto steal a wedding veil?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.91,0:14:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.08,0:14:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.59,0:14:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The inner courtyard...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.60,0:14:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry and do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if she uses a decoy\Nor some sort of camouflage...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,there's nothing to worry about!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.19,0:15:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not such a dimwit that I'd\Nbe caught with the same trick twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.71,0:15:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not falling for my tricks.\NHow boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.31,0:15:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if he's looking for a challenge,\NI'll give him one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The security is pretty bad.\NNo guards or anything so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.70,0:15:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The wedding veil and\NAsuka Jr. are waiting just for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,One small setback.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.41,0:15:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But, with the veil right in front of me,\NI can't back down now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.56,0:15:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail! You've taken the bait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.62,0:16:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Applause!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.69,0:16:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Applause, my foot!\NThat's no fair! You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.10,0:16:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go! She's going to get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Thief, take it away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.44,0:16:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,She's gonna escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.56,0:16:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don 't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.13,0:16:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Stealing this veil means Sayaka's\Nengagement will be called off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.81,0:16:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the right thing to do, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.66,0:16:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.31,0:16:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna catch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.20,0:17:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Answer me one question!\NWhy are you stealing that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.15,0:17:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you just a thief, after all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.73,0:17:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven 't you always stolen\Nto help those in trouble?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.37,0:17:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.04,0:17:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you? Why don't you\Never understand how a girl feels?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.19,0:17:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to know who\Nthe troubled one is, ask Sayaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.50,0:17:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You super-dingbat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.44,0:17:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ding... bat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.46,0:17:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,She got away again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.77,0:18:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't give up!\NI'll never give in to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.31,0:18:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.16,0:18:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So, St. Tail dissolved\Nthe engagement?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.67,0:18:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She returned the wedding veil\Nto the sender's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.38,0:18:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, he got angry\Nand called off the engagement.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.86,0:18:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much, Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.74,0:18:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's not right to thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.58,0:18:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.55,0:18:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.15,0:18:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon... cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.97,0:18:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.23,0:18:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.24,0:18:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Haneoka, what are you doing?\NHey! Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.35,0:18:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn it, why am I always\Nchasing after...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.77,0:19:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.41,0:19:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you written?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's best you don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.62,0:19:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,"I hate you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.86,0:19:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Haneoka!
